Summary:	A commonly used, MIME compliant mail and news reader
Name:		pine
Version:	4.64
Release:	38.1
License:	Freeware
URL:		https://www.washington.edu/pine
Group:		Networking/Mail
Source0:	ftp://ftp.cac.washington.edu/pine/pine%{version}.tar.bz2
